How to Setup Cron Jobs for Admin:

    Included is a file named chronograph.cron which you need to modify
    according to your settings.

Add the following jobs in the admin:

    * In Chronograph -> Jobs -> Add Job

    (a) Name: Upload To S3
        Command: upload_to_s3
        Frequency: Hourly
        Next Run: (Today)(Now)
    (b) Name: Video Daily Tasks
        Command: video_daily_tasks
        Frequency: Daily
        Next Run: (Today)(Now)
    (c) Name: Trial Expiration Check
        Command: check_trial
        Frequency: Daily
        Next Run: (Today)(Now)
